    • Method Detail

      • addAppHandler

        public static void addAppHandler(CefAppHandler appHandler)
                          throws java.lang.IllegalStateException
        Assign an AppHandler to CefApp. The AppHandler can be used to evaluate application arguments, to register your own schemes and to hook into the shutdown sequence. See CefAppHandler for more details. This method must be called before CefApp is initialized. CefApp will be initialized automatically if you call createClient() the first time.(为CefApp添加一个AppHandler。AppHandler可以用于评估应用程序参数、注册自己的schemes以及挂接到关闭序列中。有关更多详细信息，请参阅CefAppHandler。
        这个方法的调用时间必须在初始化CefApp之前(您调用了createClient()方法后CefApp会自动初始化)。)
        Parameters:
        appHandler - An instance of CefAppHandler.(appHandler-CefAppHandler的一个实例。)
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - in case of CefApp is already initialized(java.lang.IllegalStateException - CefApp已经初始化)

      • clearSchemeHandlerFactories

        public boolean clearSchemeHandlerFactories()
        Clear all registered scheme handler factories. Returns false on error. This function may be called on any thread in the browser process.(清除所有已注册的scheme处理程序，出错时返回false。此函数可以在浏览器进程中的任何线程上调用。(scheme是指http,https这样的协议头，您可以自定义一个协议头))

      • clientWasDisposed

        protected final void clientWasDisposed(CefClient client)
        This method is called by a CefClient if it was disposed. This causes CefApp to clean up its list of available client instances. If all clients are disposed, CefApp will be shutdown.(此方法由CefClient调用(如果它被释放)。这导致CefApp清理其可用客户端实例列表。如果所有客户端都已处理，则CefApp将关闭。)
        Parameters:
        client - the disposed client.(client - 已处理的客户端。)

      • createClient

        public CefClient createClient()
        Creates a new client instance and returns it to the caller. One client instance is responsible for one to many browser instances(创建一个新的客户端实例并将其返回给调用者。客户端实例与浏览器实例的关系为一对多。)
        Returns:
        a new client instance(一个新的客户端实例)

      • dispose

        public final void dispose()
        To shutdown the system, it's important to call the dispose method. Calling this method closes all client instances with and all browser instances each client owns. After that the message loop is terminated and CEF is shutdown.(调用dispose方法去关闭系统是非常重要的。调用此方法将关闭所有客户端实例以及每个客户端拥有的浏览器实例。在此之后，消息循环终止，CEF关闭。)

      • doMessageLoopWork

        public final void doMessageLoopWork(long delay_ms)
        Perform a single message loop iteration. Used on all platforms except Windows with windowed rendering.(执行单个消息循环迭代。在除了具有窗口渲染的Windows之外的所有平台上使用。)

      • handleBeforeTerminate

        protected final void handleBeforeTerminate()
        This method is invoked by the native code (currently on Mac only) in case of a termination event (e.g. someone pressed CMD+Q).(这个方法会在发生终止事件时（例如，有人按下CMD+Q）由底层代码调用（目前只发生在Mac上）。)

      • registerSchemeHandlerFactory

        public boolean registerSchemeHandlerFactory(java.lang.String schemeName,
                                            java.lang.String domainName,
                                            CefSchemeHandlerFactory factory)
        Register a scheme handler factory for the specified |scheme_name| and optional |domain_name|. An empty |domain_name| value for a standard scheme will cause the factory to match all domain names. The |domain_name| value will be ignored for non-standard schemes. If |scheme_name| is a built-in scheme and no handler is returned by |factory| then the built-in scheme handler factory will be called. If |scheme_name| is a custom scheme then also implement the CefApp::OnRegisterCustomSchemes() method in all processes. This function may be called multiple times to change or remove the factory that matches the specified |scheme_name| and optional |domain_name|. Returns false if an error occurs. This function may be called on any thread in the browser process.(为指定的|scheme_name|和可选的|domain_name|注册scheme处理程序。标准scheme的|domain_name|值为空将导致程序匹配所有域名。对于非标准scheme，将忽略|domain_name|值。如果|scheme_name|是内置方案，并且|factory|未返回任何处理程序，则将调用内置scheme处理程序。如果|scheme_name|是一个自定义scheme并且实现了CefApp:：OnRegisterCustomSchemes()方法，可以多次调用此函数来更改或删除与指定的|scheme_name|和可选的|domain_name|匹配的程序。如果发生错误，则返回false。此函数可以在浏览器进程中的任何线程上调用。(scheme是指http,https这样的协议头) )

      • startup

        public static final boolean startup(java.lang.String[] args)
        This method must be called at the beginning of the main() method to perform platform- specific startup initialization. On Linux this initializes Xlib multithreading and on macOS this dynamically loads the CEF framework.(必须在main()方法的开头调用此方法才能执行特定于平台的启动初始化。在Linux上，这将初始化Xlib多线程，而在macOS上，这会动态加载CEF框架。)
        Parameters:
        args - Command-line arguments massed to main().(args- 用于main()方法的命令行参数。)
        Returns:
        True on successful startup.(成功启动时为True。)
